        QBCC Home Warranty Insurance: What Sellers of Renovated Homes Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        If your home has had recent building work, the QBCC Home Warranty Scheme follows the property and follows you. Buyers will ask about it.
      </p>
